---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Packaging and Processing Machinery Sri Lanka | E Lanka World">
	
	<main>
		<section class="hero-container">
			<picture>
				<source srcset="/images/hero-desktop.webp" media="(min-width: 768px)" type="image/webp" />
				<img 
					src="/images/hero-mobile.webp" 
					alt="Industrial Packaging Machinery Supplier in Sri Lanka" 
					class="hero-img" 
					loading="eager"
				/>
			</picture>

			<div class="hero-overlay">
				<div class="language-stack">
					<span class="sinhala">ශ්‍රී ලංකාවේ ඇසුරුම්කරණ සහ සැකසුම් යන්ත්‍රෝපකරණ</span>
					<span class="tamil">இலங்கையில் பேக்கேஜிங் மற்றும் பதப்படுத்தும் இயந்திரங்கள்</span>
				</div>
				<h1>Packaging and Processing Machinery in Sri Lanka</h1>
				<h2>From E Lanka World International</h2>
				
				<div class="cta-group">
					<a href="https://wa.me/94776344758" class="whatsapp-btn">Inquire via WhatsApp</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="offer-section">
			<div class="container">
				<h2 class="section-title">Industrial Solutions: What We Offer</h2>
				<p class="section-subtitle">Sri Lanka's most comprehensive range of packaging and processing technology.</p>
				
				<div class="machine-grid">
					<div class="category-card">
						<div class="icon">📦</div>
						<h3>Sealing Solutions</h3>
						<ul>
							<li>Continuous Band Sealers</li>
							<li>Vertical Band Sealers</li>
							<li>Air/Nitrogen Filling Sealers</li>
							<li>Foot & Pneumatic Sealers</li>
							<li>Vacuum & Can Sealers</li>
						</ul>
					</div>

					<div class="category-card">
						<div class="icon">💧</div>
						<h3>Filling & Capping</h3>
						<ul>
							<li>Liquid & Paste Filling</li>
							<li>Powder & Granule Fillers</li>
							<li>Capping & Tin Sealing</li>
							<li>Ice Packet Machines</li>
						</ul>
					</div>

					<div class="category-card">
						<div class="icon">🔢</div>
						<h3>Coding & Packaging</h3>
						<ul>
							<li>Batch Code & Expiry Printing</li>
							<li>Strapping Machinery</li>
							<li>Shrink Tunnels</li>
							<li>Wrapping Machines</li>
						</ul>
					</div>

					<div class="category-card">
						<div class="icon">🍟</div>
						<h3>Food Processing</h3>
						<ul>
							<li>Vegetable Slicers</li>
							<li>French Fries Machines</li>
							<li>Pop Corn & Corn Removers</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="extra-offer">
					<p>...and many more specialized industrial solutions tailored for your factory.</p>
					<a href="https://wa.me/94776344758" class="secondary-btn">Request Full Catalog</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
		<section class="seo-article-section">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="article-title">Why E Lanka World International is the Best Place to Buy Machinery in Sri Lanka</h2>
        
        <div class="article-content">
            <p>
                Investing in <strong>packaging and processing machinery in Sri Lanka</strong> is a critical decision for any growing business. At <strong>E Lanka World International</strong>, we don't just sell equipment; we provide complete industrial solutions designed to increase your factory's efficiency and output. Whether you are looking for a simple hand sealer or a fully automated liquid filling line, here is why hundreds of Sri Lankan entrepreneurs trust us.
            </p>

            <div class="article-grid">
                <div class="article-text">
                    <h3>Authorized Dealer for Global Brands</h3>
                    <p>
                        We take pride in partnering with world-renowned manufacturers like <strong>Coditeck, Zodpro, and Packoni</strong>. These brands are synonymous with durability and precision. By dealing with recognized global leaders, we ensure that our customers in Sri Lanka receive the same high-standard technology used in international production lines.
                    </p>

                    <h3>Exceptional After-Sales Service & Repair</h3>
                    <p>
                        One of our core philosophies is: <strong>"We sell only what we can repair."</strong> Many importers sell machines but disappear when a technical fault occurs. At E Lanka World, our technical team is highly trained in the mechanics of every unit we sell. Our after-sales service has received immense praise from local businesses for being fast, reliable, and professional.
                    </p>

                    <h3>Unbeatable Price for Exceptional Quality</h3>
                    <p>
                        Finding a balance between cost and quality can be difficult. We offer <strong>unbeatable prices</strong> without compromising the build quality of the machinery. From <em>Batch Coding machines</em> to <em>Vacuum Packers</em>, our equipment is built to withstand the humid conditions of Sri Lanka, ensuring a long-lasting ROI for your business.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="article-text">
                    <h3>Full Stock of Spare Parts</h3>
                    <p>
                        Downtime is the enemy of production. To prevent your factory from stopping, we maintain a <strong>ready stock of all essential spare parts</strong>. Whether it is a heating element for a band sealer or a specialized nozzle for a filling machine, you won’t have to wait weeks for an international shipment.
                    </p>

                    <h3>Island-Wide Delivery & Setup</h3>
                    <p>
                        No matter where your factory is located—from Colombo to Jaffna or Matara to Batticaloa—we provide <strong>island-wide delivery</strong>. Our team ensures that your machinery arrives safely and is ready to be integrated into your production workflow immediately.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="cta-banner">
                <p>Join the community of successful Sri Lankan manufacturers using E Lanka World technology.</p>
                <a href="https://wa.me/94776344758" class="primary-btn">Contact Our Experts Today</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<section class="youtube-hub">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Product Demonstrations & Guides</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">Watch our machines in action. Select a category to see how we can automate your production.</p>
        
        <div class="video-grid">
            <div class="video-card">
                <div class="video-wrapper">
                    <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLHsqMcdTLRs7xL_hwfXXhxnuYGzamoEAv" title="Band Sealers" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen loading="lazy"></iframe>
                </div>
                <h3>Band Sealers</h3>
            </div>

            <div class="video-card">
                <div class="video-wrapper">
                    <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLHsqMcdTLRs59RNdf-zEngIY5tNEeSOEE" title="Date Coding Machines" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen loading="lazy"></iframe>
                </div>
                <h3>Date Coding & Online TIJ</h3>
            </div>

            <div class="video-card">
                <div class="video-wrapper">
                    <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLHsqMcdTLRs40gR_huQUzfeKYRcX4w_Ur" title="Liquid Filling" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen loading="lazy"></iframe>
                </div>
                <h3>Liquid Filling Solutions</h3>
            </div>

            <div class="video-card">
                <div class="video-wrapper">
                    <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLHsqMcdTLRs5Uh6Kw5GQzlNlIZHnUbwt2" title="Vacuum Sealers" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen loading="lazy"></iframe>
                </div>
                <h3>Vacuum Packaging</h3>
            </div>

            <div class="video-card">
                <div class="video-wrapper">
                    <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLHsqMcdTLRs4yAX5aYvlxMEdacIJOlYqS" title="Weighing & Filling" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen loading="lazy"></iframe>
                </div>
                <h3>Weighing & Filling</h3>
            </div>

            <div class="video-card">
                <div class="video-wrapper">
                    <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLHsqMcdTLRs7b1dZ7qwqUEKfuj1HWTIyt" title="Can Sealers" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen loading="lazy"></iframe>
                </div>
                <h3>Tin & Can Sealing</h3>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="more-videos">
            <h4>More Specialized Machinery Playlists:</h4>
            <div class="tag-cloud">
                <a href="https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLHsqMcdTLRs7M5YmvCsBBYPI6SgFnfcnE" target="_blank">Handheld Laser Printing</a>
                <a href="https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLHsqMcdTLRs6Z3P78Q8NteGfwsQ0yEPw_" target="_blank">Label Printing</a>
                <a href="https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLHsqMcdTLRs5TDEwBulU9ZYiogJAOHKEw" target="_blank">Mini Inkjet Printers</a>
                <a href="https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLHsqMcdTLRs6AN35dWRM-VXDPVEcdujlQ" target="_blank">Induction Sealing</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="cta-footer">
            <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@atlaslanka2116" target="_blank" class="channel-btn">Visit Our Full Channel</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
	</main>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* HERO STYLES */
  .hero-container {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    min-height: 80vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-img {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-overlay {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); /* Slightly more opaque for better contrast */
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 15px;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 1rem;
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  h1 { font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 3rem); margin: 0.5rem 0; color: #001f3f; line-height: 1.2; }
  h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; color: #2563eb; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; }
  
  .language-stack span { display: block; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #4b5563; margin-bottom: 4px; }

  .whatsapp-btn {
    background: #25D366;
    color: white;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
    display: inline-block;
    transition: transform 0.2s;
  }
  .whatsapp-btn:hover { transform: scale(1.05); }

  /* OFFER SECTION STYLES */
  .offer-section { padding: 6rem 1.5rem; background-color: #f8fafc; }
  .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; }
  
  .section-title { font-size: 2.5rem; color: #001f3f; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .section-subtitle { color: #64748b; margin-bottom: 4rem; font-size: 1.1rem; }

 /* 1. Default for Desktop (Large Screens) */
  .machine-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); /* Forces 4 columns in 1 row */
      gap: 1.5rem;
      text-align: left;
  }

  .category-card {
      background: white;
      padding: 2.5rem;
      border-radius: 15px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
      border-top: 5px solid #2563eb;
      transition: translateY 0.3s;
  }
  .category-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); }

  .icon { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  
  h3 { color: #001f3f; font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; border-bottom: 2px solid #f1f5f9; padding-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  
  ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
  ul li { 
      padding: 0.5rem 0; 
      color: #475569; 
      font-size: 1rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
  }
  ul li::before { content: "✔"; color: #2563eb; margin-right: 12px; font-weight: bold; }

  .extra-offer { margin-top: 5rem; font-style: italic; color: #64748b; }
  
  .secondary-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      color: #2563eb;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      border: 2px solid #2563eb;
      padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      transition: all 0.3s;
  }
  .secondary-btn:hover { background: #2563eb; color: white; }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .hero-container { min-height: 70vh; }
    .hero-overlay { padding: 1.5rem; }
    .section-title { font-size: 2rem; }
  }

  /* 2. For Tablets and Large Mobiles (2 columns, 2 rows) */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .machine-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); /* 2 columns */
    }
    .section-title { font-size: 2.2rem; }
  }

  /* 3. For Small Mobiles (Stay 2 columns or drop to 1 if too cramped) */
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .machine-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); /* Keeps 2 columns for symmetry */
        gap: 1rem; /* Tighter gap for small screens */
    }
    .category-card { padding: 1.5rem; } /* Reduce padding so content fits */
    h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; }
    ul li { font-size: 0.85rem; }
  }

  /* SEO ARTICLE STYLES */
  .seo-article-section {
      padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: #334155;
  }
  .seo-article-section .container { 
      max-width: 1100px; 
      margin: 0 auto; 
  }
  
  .article-title {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      color: #001f3f;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      font-weight: 800;
  }

  .article-content p {
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .article-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      text-align: left;
  }

  .article-text h3 {
      color: #2563eb;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      border: none; /* Resetting any previous h3 borders */
  }

  .seo-article-section strong { color: #0f172a; }

  .cta-banner {
      margin-top: 4rem;
      background: #f1f5f9;
      padding: 3rem;
      border-radius: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border: 2px dashed #cbd5e1;
  }

  .cta-banner .primary-btn {
      background: #001f3f;
      color: white;
      padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 1rem;
      transition: background 0.3s ease;
  }

  .cta-banner .primary-btn:hover {
      background: #2563eb;
  }

  /* Responsive for Mobile */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .article-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1rem; }
      .article-title { font-size: 1.8rem; }
      .cta-banner { padding: 1.5rem; }
  }

  /* YOUTUBE HUB STYLES */
  .youtube-hub {
      padding: 6rem 1.5rem;
      background-color: #0f172a;
      color: white;
  }
  .youtube-hub .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; }
  .youtube-hub .section-title { color: #ffffff; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .youtube-hub .section-subtitle { color: #94a3b8; margin-bottom: 4rem; }

  .video-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); /* 3 columns on Desktop */
      gap: 2rem;
  }

  .video-card {
      background: #1e293b;
      padding: 0.8rem;
      border-radius: 12px;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }
  .video-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); }

  .video-wrapper {
      position: relative;
      padding-bottom: 56.25%; /* 16:9 Aspect Ratio */
      height: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 8px;
  }
  .video-wrapper iframe {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
  }

  .video-card h3 {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-top: 1rem;
      color: #3b82f6;
  }

  /* Tag Cloud for extra playlists */
  .more-videos { margin-top: 4rem; border-top: 1px solid #334155; padding-top: 3rem; }
  .more-videos h4 { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: #94a3b8; }
  
  .tag-cloud {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 1rem;
  }
  .tag-cloud a {
      background: #334155;
      color: #e2e8f0;
      padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
      border-radius: 50px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      transition: background 0.3s;
  }
  .tag-cloud a:hover { background: #2563eb; color: white; }

  .cta-footer { margin-top: 4rem; }
  .channel-btn {
      background: #ff0000;
      color: white;
      padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      display: inline-block;
  }

  /* RESPONSIVE BREAKPOINTS */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      .video-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } /* 2 columns on Tablet */
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .video-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } /* 1 column on Mobile */
      .youtube-hub { padding: 4rem 1rem; }
  }

</style>